21:51.160 --> 21:52.350
Apa ini?

21:52.650 --> 21:54.170
Bandar Shangdu...

21:54.200 --> 21:55.310
Xia Xiaolan?

21:56.640 --> 21:57.960
Hebatnya, abang.

21:58.550 --> 22:00.000
Usaha abang berbaloi.

22:00.550 --> 22:01.240
Dia sekarang

22:01.240 --> 22:02.960
