27:13.270 --> 27:13.870
Tao, mari.

27:14.240 --> 27:14.790
Cantik.

27:37.030 --> 27:38.160
Kenapa awak senyum?

27:40.640 --> 27:42.270
Saya tengok awak

27:42.300 --> 27:43.480
