28:03.160 --> 28:04.590
Saya takut awak terbau nanti.

28:04.590 --> 28:05.000
Baik.

28:12.580 --> 28:14.700
[Kepada Xia Xiaolan]

28:19.270 --> 28:20.000
Abang Jianhua.

28:20.000 --> 28:21.400
